<div id="review_2577985070" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2577985070" />
    <a title="8th Day Reads" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/74583594-8th-day-reads"><img alt="8th Day Reads" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1512397836p2/74583594.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2577985070?book_show_action=true">Oct 30, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="8th Day Reads" class="user" itemprop="url" name="8th Day Reads" href="/user/show/74583594-8th-day-reads">8th Day Reads</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2577985070" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6579418008019658309">Aimee Cabo Nikolov’s Love is the Answer God is the Cure is not what I was expecting. It’s a heart-wrenching real life account of one woman’s struggles against the odds stacked against her throughout her life and the salvation of finding true love. <br/><br/>Nikolov has gone through so much, all chronicled here. As a reader I was stunned by each additional hurdle she was faced with. In a horror novel a character may be relentlessly pursued by the stuff of nightmares but Nikolov had this for real. I couldn’</span>
  <span id="freeText6579418008019658309" style="display:none">Aimee Cabo Nikolov’s Love is the Answer God is the Cure is not what I was expecting. It’s a heart-wrenching real life account of one woman’s struggles against the odds stacked against her throughout her life and the salvation of finding true love. <br /><br />Nikolov has gone through so much, all chronicled here. As a reader I was stunned by each additional hurdle she was faced with. In a horror novel a character may be relentlessly pursued by the stuff of nightmares but Nikolov had this for real. I couldn’t help but feel for her, although her writing never comes across as attention-seeking or like she’s competing to be seen as worse off than anyone else. <br /><br />Despite its contents this is not a depressing read, but a story of courage and of a journey and it shows that love can ultimately triumph. <br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="6579418008019658309" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


