              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8426823382917511130">This is a heart-wrenching memoir about the authors everyday struggle of surviving childhood abuse and sexual assault throughout her life. She has had a hard life - being shunned by family, homeless, drugs, custody battles, etc. - and yet she persevered. <br/><br/>This book seems like a coping mechanism, a way to tell her story to many. How she persevered through it all, I could not imagine, but she always kept faith even through the worst of times. <br/><br/>If you like to read stories of survivals, you will enjoy </span>
  <span id="freeText8426823382917511130" style="display:none">This is a heart-wrenching memoir about the authors everyday struggle of surviving childhood abuse and sexual assault throughout her life. She has had a hard life - being shunned by family, homeless, drugs, custody battles, etc. - and yet she persevered. <br /><br />This book seems like a coping mechanism, a way to tell her story to many. How she persevered through it all, I could not imagine, but she always kept faith even through the worst of times. <br /><br />If you like to read stories of survivals, you will enjoy this book. It is easy to read, but does at times overlap timelines. But all in all, this story is a must read to learn about how childhood abuse and sexual assault can affect someone’s life forever and how with a little faith and love things can turn around.</span>
