<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer8411649268586438141">Aimee Cabo Nikolov is a Cuban American who has lived most of her life in Miami. She is a speaker, trained nurse and the president and owner of IMIC, Inc, a medical research company in Palmetto Bay. <br/>Aimee is also the host of &quot;The Cure with Aimee Cabo&quot;, a nationally syndicated live radio show, and later a podcast. <a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='https://aimeespurpose.com'>https://aimeespurpose.com</a><br/><br/>She lives with her husband, Dr. Boris Nikolov, and two of her</span>
  <span id="freeText8411649268586438141" style="display:none">Aimee Cabo Nikolov is a Cuban American who has lived most of her life in Miami. She is a speaker, trained nurse and the president and owner of IMIC, Inc, a medical research company in Palmetto Bay. <br />Aimee is also the host of "The Cure with Aimee Cabo", a nationally syndicated live radio show, and later a podcast. <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://aimeespurpose.com">https://aimeespurpose.com</a><br /><br />She lives with her husband, Dr. Boris Nikolov, and two of her children, Sean and Michelle. This is her first book. The book won several awards - Pinnacle, NYC Big book award, Feathered Quill Gold/1st place. <br />The Second book is inspired by her work at the radio show and is a compilation of Christian poems based on popular songs.</span>
